      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.BiLTxWD0s3JPqLHZ]{Gloom Gunner}</p>\n<p>If you score a critical hit with a weapon you wield, you can apply the critical hit effect of the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.equipment.Item.nsQhsNOgfUYvLQIc]{Ominous} fusion in addition to one other critical hit effect the weapon has. When you render a target @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.nywSVEeDvp1bk7L3]{Shaken}, you can spend 1 Resolve Point to change that condition to @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.DtwiUWi8dpzkq4tM]{Frightened} for the same duration. In addition, once per day when you fail a saving throw against a mind-affecting effect, you can reroll that saving throw.</p>"
